KaptioTravel__PackageInformation__c.Name: Important Information
KaptioTravel__PackageInformation__c.KaptioTravel__Value__c:
Some things to note:

  • Should you not be travelling on the group tour flights, shared bus transfers will be used between the hotel and the airport for the departure transfer.
  • On Day 5 we will be visiting a traditional Korean spa. Please remember to pack your swimwear.
  • On Day 12 we will be visiting the Demilitarised Zone (DMZ). Please remember to bring your passport.
  • Entry into the DMZ is subject to local conditions and the availability of tickets, which cannot be pre-purchased. Therefore, the exact sightseeing on the day and places visited may vary (included in itinerary on Day 12).
  • On Day 20 we will be travelling by bullet train and our luggage will be transferred via coach. Please pack an overnight bag with one night's worth of luggage. Unfortunately, bullet trains have very limited space for luggage.
  • On Day 23 we will be travelling by bullet train and our luggage will be transferred via coach. Please pack an overnight bag with two night's worth of luggage. Unfortunately, bullet trains have very limited space for luggage.
  • From June 2019, Miyajima's famous floating Torii Gate is undergoing renovations. During the renovation works, the Torii Gate will be covered under partially transparent scaffolding. A bridge is being built on the left side of the gate to aid the renovation works.
